{"sample_id": "coherence_xuanhuan_023", "genre": "xuanhuan", "difficulty": "medium", "input": {"preceding_context": "叶辰进入了一个远古秘境，里面有无数的机关陷阱。他凭借前世的记忆一一避开。", "user_request": "请续写接下来的情节"}, "output": {"text": "但他发现记忆中的秘境地图和实际地形有出入——原来秘境每隔一千年会重新变化一次布局。他不得不在记忆中寻找规律，重新绘制地图。"}, "reference": {"coherence_score": 4, "rationale": "记忆优势-意外变化-重新适应，合理转折", "contradiction_types": [], "expected_behavior": ""}, "evaluation": {"narrative_coherence": 4, "plot_continuity": 5, "world_consistency": 5, "genre_fidelity": 5, "faithfulness": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "context_recall": 0.85}, "negative_sample": false, "error_type": null}
