{"sample_id": "coherence_xuanhuan_026", "genre": "xuanhuan", "difficulty": "easy", "input": {"preceding_context": "叶辰在街上遇到一个乞丐，乞丐伸手向他讨钱。叶辰看乞丐可怜，给了他一两银子。", "user_request": "请续写接下来的情节"}, "output": {"text": "乞丐接过银子，突然抬头看了叶辰一眼，眼中精光一闪。乞丐低声说：年轻人，你我有缘，送你一句话——三天后别去城北。说完乞丐就消失了。"}, "reference": {"coherence_score": 5, "rationale": "偶遇-施舍-得到神秘警告，铺垫感强", "contradiction_types": [], "expected_behavior": ""}, "evaluation": {"narrative_coherence": 5, "plot_continuity": 5, "world_consistency": 5, "genre_fidelity": 5, "faithfulness": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "context_recall": 0.85}, "negative_sample": false, "error_type": null}
{"sample_id": "coherence_xuanhuan_027", "genre": "xuanhuan", "difficulty": "medium", "input": {"preceding_context": "叶辰在拍卖会上看中了一瓶龙血，但竞拍价格高得离谱。他的钱不够。", "user_request": "请续写接下来的情节"}, "output": {"text": "叶辰在最后一刻拿出了一颗前世炼制的丹药，说要用丹药换龙血。拍卖师鉴定后发现是失传已久的九转还魂丹，价值远在龙血之上。交易成功。"}, "reference": {"coherence_score": 4, "rationale": "想买-钱不够-用丹药交换-成功", "contradiction_types": [], "expected_behavior": ""}, "evaluation": {"narrative_coherence": 4, "plot_continuity": 5, "world_consistency": 5, "genre_fidelity": 5, "faithfulness": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "context_recall": 0.85}, "negative_sample": false, "error_type": null}
{"sample_id": "coherence_xuanhuan_028", "genre": "xuanhuan", "difficulty": "easy", "input": {"preceding_context": "系统提示：检测到附近有隐藏任务——帮李寡妇找回丢失的猫。", "user_request": "请续写接下来的情节"}, "output": {"text": "叶辰嘴角抽了抽：我一个重生帝尊，你让我找猫？但系统说奖励是20积分，他只好去了。他用神识一扫就在隔壁院子找到了猫。任务完成。"}, "reference": {"coherence_score": 5, "rationale": "接到低级任务-吐槽-用神识轻松完成", "contradiction_types": [], "expected_behavior": ""}, "evaluation": {"narrative_coherence": 5, "plot_continuity": 5, "world_consistency": 5, "genre_fidelity": 5, "faithfulness": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "context_recall": 0.85}, "negative_sample": false, "error_type": null}
{"sample_id": "coherence_xuanhuan_029", "genre": "xuanhuan", "difficulty": "easy", "input": {"preceding_context": "叶辰在修炼时发现丹田中多了一团金色的雾气，他前世从没见过这种情况。", "user_request": "请续写接下来的情节"}, "output": {"text": "他小心翼翼地将神识探入金色雾气中，突然一股庞大的信息涌入了他的脑海——那是一篇上古神魔修炼功法。金色雾气就是功法的载体。"}, "reference": {"coherence_score": 5, "rationale": "修炼中的意外-探索-获得传承", "contradiction_types": [], "expected_behavior": ""}, "evaluation": {"narrative_coherence": 5, "plot_continuity": 5, "world_consistency": 5, "genre_fidelity": 5, "faithfulness": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "context_recall": 0.85}, "negative_sample": false, "error_type": null}
{"sample_id": "coherence_xuanhuan_030", "genre": "xuanhuan", "difficulty": "medium", "input": {"preceding_context": "王猛被人下了毒，生命垂危。解药需要一味极其稀有的药材——千年血灵芝。", "user_request": "请续写接下来的情节"}, "output": {"text": "叶辰记得前世在幽冥谷见过一株血灵芝。他连夜赶往幽冥谷，在谷中与守护灵兽大战一场，最终拿到了血灵芝。赶回来时王猛只剩一口气了。"}, "reference": {"coherence_score": 4, "rationale": "中毒-寻找解药-战斗-及时赶回，紧张但略显套路", "contradiction_types": [], "expected_behavior": ""}, "evaluation": {"narrative_coherence": 4, "plot_continuity": 5, "world_consistency": 5, "genre_fidelity": 5, "faithfulness": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "context_recall": 0.85}, "negative_sample": false, "error_type": null}
